	   <tr><td colspan=2>well i was level 27 my guild took me to upper Guk for the camp. we had 1 warrior lvl 30, 1 cleric lvl 31, 1 druid lvl 29, rouges lvl 45 and 30, and a mag lvl 30. everyone got exp there except the 45 and after 6 wonderful hours i got ghoulbane. i was the only one to die while we were there, so not all that bad of a trip. for those of you who dont have it, get it this weapon rocks i am now lvl 29 it procs once a battle for 150 dmg with 111 str plus yaulp i can hit for on avg 45. this sword is worth it if you are on the saryrn server give me a tell ill help you get it. you must have friends there to help you. <br>&nbsp;<br>Celtpirate Waverider<br>34 paladin<br>saryrn-Boche Morte<br>Yoshiro<br>15 cleric<br>saryrn-House of Wargoth</td></tr>
